name: complex_if_compare_common_right_lt
section: control-if-order
args: cond:Bool common:Int a:Int b:Int
type: Bool
expect: True
description: Less-than from an if expression to a common right operand must choose branchwise comparisons.
law: (= (fuzz-lt? (if {cond} {a} {b}) {common}) (if {cond} (fuzz-lt? {a} {common}) (fuzz-lt? {b} {common})))
